---
const cities = [
  {
    city: 'Tegucigalpa',
    dept: 'Francisco Morazán',
    code: 'TGU',
    featured: false,
    places: [
      { name: 'Carnicería El Corte', type: 'Carnicería' },
    ],
  },
  {
    city: 'Gracias',
    dept: 'Lempira',
    code: 'GRA',
    featured: true,
    places: [
      { name: 'Texaco Las Torres',        type: 'Estación' },
      { name: 'Supermercado Denisse',     type: 'Supermercado' },
      { name: 'Minisuper Yaqui',          type: 'Minisuper' },
      { name: 'Supermercado Sarahi',      type: 'Supermercado' },
      { name: 'Supermercado Mi Súper',    type: 'Supermercado' },
      { name: 'Market Punto Básico',      type: 'Market' },
      { name: 'Inversiones DAYSA',        type: 'Distribuidora' },
      { name: 'Restaurante Villa Alicia', type: 'Restaurante' },
    ],
  },
  {
    city: 'Lepaera',
    dept: 'Lempira',
    code: 'LPA',
    featured: false,
    places: [
      { name: "Elena's Bakery", type: 'Panadería' },
    ],
  },
];

const totalPlaces = cities.reduce((n, c) => n + c.places.length, 0);
---

<section class="stores" id="proveedores">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">08 / Dónde encontrarlo</span>
        <h2>Encuéntralo<br/><em>aquí cerca.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Pikanté ya está en pulperías, supermercados y restaurantes de tu zona. Si no lo ves en tu tiendita, pídelo — andamos creciendo.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stores-block reveal">
      <div class="stores-block-head">
        <h3>Puntos de <em>venta</em></h3>
        <div class="meta">
          <span><b>{cities.length}</b> ciudades</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span><b>{totalPlaces}</b> puntos activos</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>Actualizado · May 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-grid">
        {cities.map((c, i) => (
          <article
            class={`city-card reveal${c.featured ? ' is-featured' : ''}`}
            style={`transition-delay:${i * 0.06}s`}
          >
            <header class="city-card-head">
              <span class="city-code">/ {c.code}</span>
              <div class="city-name">
                <h4>{c.city}</h4>
                <span class="city-dept">{c.dept}</span>
              </div>
              <span class="city-count" aria-label={`${c.places.length} puntos`}>
                <b>{String(c.places.length).padStart(2, '0')}</b>
                <em>punto{c.places.length > 1 ? 's' : ''}</em>
              </span>
            </header>

            <ul class="city-places">
              {c.places.map((p) => (
                <li class="place">
                  <span class="place-pin" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M12 22s7-7.5 7-13a7 7 0 1 0-14 0c0 5.5 7 13 7 13z"/>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.4"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="place-body">
                    <b class="place-name">{p.name}</b>
                    <span class="place-type">{p.type}</span>
                  </span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA — proveedor -->
    <div class="stores-cta reveal">
      <div class="stores-cta-text">
        <h4>¿Tienes una tiendita? <em>Véndela.</em></h4>
        <p>Únete a la red de proveedores Pikanté. Margen catracho, entregas directas y material para que tu pulpería se prenda.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/+50497864648" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Quiero vender Pikanté
        <span class="arrow">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
